{"id":30392,"type":6,"name":"元禄繚乱","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/63/e8/30392_ULHA8.jpg","summary":"　　元禄缭乱是1999年的大河剧，播出期间是1999年1月10日－12月12日。以忠臣藏故事做题材的大河剧有1964年的赤穗浪士、1975年的元禄太平记、1982年的山顶的群像，而本剧是第四度将忠臣藏搬上大河剧系列的作品。\r\n　　女星、铃木保奈美在本剧演出后引退。2011年大河剧“江～公主们的战国～”复出。\r\n\r\n　　忠臣蔵をテーマにした大河ドラマの4作目。華やかな文化が生まれ、政治経済が乱れた5代将軍綱吉の元禄時代。君主・浅野内匠頭の刃傷事件を発端に、大石内蔵助ら赤穂浪士の討ち入りまでの日々を描く。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>元禄缭乱</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>日曜日</li><li><span>制作: </span><a href=\"/person/974\">NHK</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>49回</li><li><span>开始: </span>1999年1月10日</li><li><span>结束: </span>1999年12月12日</li><li><span>类型: </span>大河ドラマ</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>45分钟</li><li><span>频道: </span>NHK</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"忠臣藏","count":1},{"name":"江户时代","count":1},{"name":"元禄缭乱","count":1},{"name":"1999","count":1},{"name":"大河剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":140932,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140932","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140933,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140933","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140934,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140934","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140935,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140935","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140936,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140936","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140937,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140937","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140938,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/140938","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":140939,"url